  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "Pipulate is a **local-first, single-tenant desktop app framework** featuring AI-assisted, step-by-step workflows. Designed to feel like an Electron app, it uniquely runs a full, reproducible Linux environment within a project folder using Nix, ensuring consistency across macOS, Linux, and Windows (via WSL).",
    "context": "![Pipulate Free & Open Source SEO with & for LLMs](https://github.com/miklevin/pipulate/raw/main/assets/images/ai-seo-software.png)\n\n> **Your data. Your AI. Your machine. Your control.**  \n> No subscriptions, no vendor lock-in, no cloud costs.",
    "cynefinDomain": "complex"
  },
